The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Nation | Aradhana director dead
                                                                                                               Aradhana director dead
                            
	Mumbai, April 9 (PTI): Filmmaker Shakti Samanta today died after a brief illness. He was 83.        
	He passed away around 5pm at his suburban Santacruz residence. He was recovering from a stroke he had suffered over two months ago, a family member said.        
	Samanta had directed box-office hits like Kati Patang, Amar Prem and Aradhana, all starring Rajesh Khanna.                                                                                                                                                                            
